title: Chile Three Month Interbank Rate
description: Chile Three Month Interbank Rate was at 11.75 percent on Wednesday November 9. Interbank Rate in Chile averaged 2.61 percent from 2002 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 11.86 percent in October of 2022 and a record low of 0.06 percent in August of 2009. In Chile, the interbank rate is the rate of interest charged on short-term loans made between banks. This page provides - Chile Overnight Interbank Rate - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Chilean Benchmark Facility
